options.name: Pipe Size
description: 1.5" Standard theatrical pipe size (1.9" OD), rated for 30 pounds per foot.
2" pipe size (2.375" OD) is extra strong, rated for 50 pounds per foot. "MAY NOT FIT ALL CLAMP SIZES"

options.name: Color
description: Black is standard
White will add a few days to production time.
Custom colors are available but add cost and production time to your order.

options.name: Total Length
description: Any multiple of 16" up to 100'. It may be easier to install multiple shorter MEGABATTENS.

options.name: Number of Power Circuits
description: 1 to 6 circuits available, more than 4 circuits adds some extra cost. 6-16 LED fixtures can typically run on one 20 amp circuit.

options.name: Power Input Type
description: Wire Leads to be run in customer supplied metallic flex or conduit for permanent wiring to customers junction box.
19 pin Circular connector allows temporary connection of up to 6 circuits.
Wire Whips allows easy connection of up to 3 circuits with customer installed plugs.
Junction Box has wiring space for electrical connections for connecting permanent wiring from building.
Double selections add an additional power input to the opposite side of the MEGABATTEN.

options.name: Power Lead or Whip Lenght
description: Length of leads or whip extending out of the MegaBatten for wiring. Shorter is usually better and less expensive.

options.name: Data Input/Output Type
description: RJ-45 is easily installed on Cat 5 wiring.
5 pin XLR is the DMX standard.
3 pin XLR is often used on import fixtures.

options.name: End Cap Type
description: Flat caps are used when an inch really matters.
Rounded caps are standard.

options.name: DMX Splitter
description: Flat caps are used when an inch really matters.
Rounded caps are standard.
